{"tid":1161550,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"何猷君戀愛巷塗鴉示愛惹爭議 文綺華︰與文化局商討是否觸法","createTime":"2019-05-19T09:18:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T11:17:28.000Z","uid":25659,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"29f5b69b99feb149b6c12baec981f4aac6087418","tid":1161550,"uid":25659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T09:18:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/05/19/171716_30d15c78ccfcf7d6f875a29ddae653a1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F05%2F19%2F171716_30d15c78ccfcf7d6f875a29ddae653a1.png&h=85f46f10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/05/19/171719_7267a220b4e46dc57c36736550c82b63.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F05%2F19%2F171719_7267a220b4e46dc57c36736550c82b63.png&h=b431f4e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n賭王何鴻燊四房兒子何猷君早前求婚成功，近日網上廣泛流傳二人在國內明星相親節目《愛的時差》其中一段片段，片中所見何猷君在大三巴下戀愛巷一幅牆壁上塗鴉，向奚夢瑤示愛。而戀愛巷為本澳文物建築，有關片段引起坊間熱議。<br />\n<br />\n旅遊局局長文綺華受訪時稱，事發在世遺城區，有關行為會否抵觸法律，會同文化局等相關部門商討。她稱，拍攝許可一般須向文化局申請，並非旅遊局權限。她亦提醒旅客及市民，胡亂塗鴉可觸犯法律。<br />\n<br />\n至於有關行為會否因「明星效應」向旅客帶出錯誤訊息？文綺華表示，當局與其他部門已計劃了一段時間，針對旅客「一籃子」宣傳控煙、負責任博彩等的重要訊息，正計劃推出小冊子或在官方帳號上宣傳，希望旅客不要將當地習慣帶到澳門，避免因一時興起而誤墮法網。<br />\n<br />\n(節錄)<br />\n<br />\n全文︰<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2EiqyY6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2EiqyY6&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPebr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=c2223493\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2EiqyY6</a>"},{"pid":"0af776ac5a90bbfecf9c9a9423f2de3ef6f514e3","tid":1161550,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T09:19:14.000Z","msg":"班官頭都㾗埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b56401ad3fca429070bd7c3c21b993c581f71c2","tid":1161550,"uid":25659,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T09:20:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/05/19/172021_55e99deecad6117caec2b1c155b76c35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F05%2F19%2F172021_55e99deecad6117caec2b1c155b76c35.jpg&h=4ab39b2c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"84f958f2a2972b2ad61b5b51957fac8d67a4b9ff","tid":1161550,"uid":8810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T09:22:34.000Z","msg":"之後咪又不了了之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7321934233a48307d03c67a3338745503777aea3","tid":1161550,"uid":201074,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T09:23:01.000Z","msg":"D字仲肉酸過小學生寫既字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daecc3b935feb07b0b838a010f8d494298e5799e","tid":1161550,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T09:25:46.000Z","msg":"er er有錢人不在此限"},{"pid":"f6b0e7156439da18403e9b85be9a27cebc422efd","tid":1161550,"uid":27038,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T09:27:33.000Z","msg":"屌你，成案例，如果無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以後遊客去澳門寫爆幅牆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3731bbc8d09ee67384dc5adc056450d0232a5bd","tid":1161550,"uid":42578,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"4b56401ad3fca429070bd7c3c21b993c581f71c2","tid":1161550,"uid":25659,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T09:20:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/05/19/172021_55e99deecad6117caec2b1c155b76c35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F05%2F19%2F172021_55e99deecad6117caec2b1c155b76c35.jpg&h=4ab39b2c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T09:29:24.000Z","msg":"No✅"},{"pid":"d0c99f8aa9f59c2089a0902e7ceb4f7a96c30ac9","tid":1161550,"uid":111270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit